definitions.definition: A sled used to go down a bob track.
The sport of travelling down a bob track as fast as possible.
A short sled, mostly used as one of a pair connected by a reach or coupling ; the compound sled so formed.

main_definition: ( US and Canada ) A sled used to go down a bob track.
secondary_definitions: ( uncountable , US and Canada ) The sport of travelling down a bob track as fast as possible.
A short sled, mostly used as one of a pair connected by a reach or coupling ; the compound sled so formed.
